 Next\nLeft = Previous", "short_description": "Tripeaks Solitaire card game with beautiful graphics and unique environment in VR!\n\nFull Oculus Quest/Quest 2 Controller support!\n\n150 different card layouts!"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "132448825394132", "locale": "de_DE", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "TripeaksDreamland VR", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Tripeaks Solitaire Kartenspiel mit wundersch\u00f6nen Grafiken in VR!\n\nFeatures:\n- Volle Oculus Quest/Quest 2 VR-Controller Unterst\u00fctzung\n- Drei Schwierigkeiten\n- Smoothe Grafiken\n- Online-Highscores\n- 150 Levels mit unterschiedlichen Layouts\n- 5 Sprachen w\u00e4hlbar (englisch, deutsch, spanisch, t\u00fcrkisch, polnisch)\n\nTouch Thumbsticks verwenden um die Musik zu steuern:\nDr\u00fccken= Start/Stop\nHoch = Lautst\u00e4rke erh\u00f6hen\nRunter = Lautst\u00e4rke verringern\nRechts = N\u00e4chster Song\nLinks = Vorheriger Song", "short_description": "Tripeaks Solitaire Kartenspiel mit wundersch\u00f6nen Grafiken und einzigartiger Umgebung in VR!\n\nVolle Oculus Quest/Quest 2 Controller Unterst\u00fctzung!\n\n150 verschiedene Kartenlayouts!"}]}, "developer_name": "Daniel Ali", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.privacypolicies.com/live/a91d69a4-a73e-47e8-bbf3-bfc66283ec47", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Daniel Ali", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://discord.gg/tNAsJzz6", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1676485315806614"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ARCADE", "CASUAL", "PUZZLE"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "d